title: Weekend chat to Harry Enfield and Paul Whitehouse ahead of first UK tour
text:
Tweet 
In it, we interview Harry Enfield and Paul Whitehouse who are taking to the road for their first ever UK tour. Not a lot of people know that. 
We also chat to interior design delight Linda Barker about being fabulous in her fifties and making a splash. How does it feel to be named one of the sexiest women in the world? What do you think?
